OL,3,CSwimming pools to reopen after fault
OL,4,Cwith main safety switch
OL,6,FBeau Sejour pools in Guernsey are set
OL,7,Fto welcome back swimmers after they
OL,8,Fclosed suddenly on Friday (12
OL,9,FSeptember).
OL,11,FAn unexpected fault was found in the
OL,12,Ffacility's main safety switch, which
OL,13,Fcontrols essential functions such as
OL,14,Fthe level of chlorine in the water.
OL,16,FAt the time, the Head of Recreation
OL,17,FServices, Sam Herridge, said:
OL,18,F"Fortunately, the issue was discovered
OL,19,Fwhilst chlorine levels in the pools
OL,20,Fwere normal.
