OL,4,Cwith main safety switch
OL,6,F"We appreciate this will cause
OL,7,Fdisruption for many people and are
OL,8,Fvery sorry to anyone who is impacted.
OL,9,FHowever, the safety of all our
OL,10,Fswimmers is our absolute priority and
OL,11,Fwe cannot reopen until we are
OL,12,Fconfident it is safe to do so."
OL,14,FIn an update on Monday, he added that
OL,15,Frepairs are close to being finished,
OL,16,Ffollowing work with a specialist UK
OL,17,Fcontractor.
